					<div class="author-info">
						
						<h4>Tom Rowe</h4>
						<p>Tom is a writer of short stories, poetry, novels and the column Hell Over Heels here on The Carouser...all those things writers do. He just writes them all hazily in a bar and then puts them on http://www.not-dark-yet.com/ .

He edits when he is sober and rarely does he edit.</p>
						
